{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO849474B0481P0D1N001066", "chronotag": "1742487568554", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CS1066", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1066", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CSVIEECO", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO419610B0481P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0481", "triAmendement": "ebiaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaanw", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA267200", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845407", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Huyghe"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 10", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 10", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 10", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0481.asp#D_Article_10"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": "Apres", "numero": "2", "alineaDesignation": "Apr\u00e8s l'alin\u00e9a 2"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": "Sous r\u00e9serve de son traitement par les services de l'Assembl\u00e9e nationale et de sa recevabilit\u00e9", "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apr&#x00E8;s l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;2, ins&#x00E9;rer l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a suivant&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;1&#x00B0;&nbsp;A Au 2&#x00B0;&nbsp;de l&#x2019;article L.&nbsp;821&#x2011;6,&nbsp;la premi&#x00E8;re occurrence des mots&nbsp;:&#x00AB;&nbsp;des m&#x00EA;mes peines&nbsp;&#x00BB; est remplac&#x00E9;e par les mots&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;d&#x2019;une peine d&#x2019;amende de 30&nbsp;000&nbsp;euros&nbsp;&#x00BB;&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>L&#x2019;ordonnance de transposition n&#x00B0; 2023-1142 du 6 d&#x00E9;cembre 2023 avait pour objectif de transposer la directive n&#x00B0;2022/2464, dite &#x00AB;&nbsp;Directive CSRD&nbsp;&#x00BB;. Or, une de ses dispositions revient &#x00E0; surtransposer cette directive. <br>&nbsp;<br>La directive pr&#x00E9;voyait la d&#x00E9;signation d&#x2019;un v&#x00E9;rificateur de durabilit&#x00E9;. L&#x2019;ordonnance a, elle, introduit la p&#x00E9;nalisation de l&#x2019;absence de cette d&#x00E9;signation. Cette disposition n&#x2019;&#x00E9;tait pas pr&#x00E9;vue par la&nbsp;&#x00AB;&nbsp;Directive CSRD&nbsp;&#x00BB;. L&#x2019;ordonnance d&#x00E9;passe donc le cadre fix&#x00E9; par le texte europ&#x00E9;en. <br>&nbsp;<br>Dans une d&#x00E9;marche de simplification des normes pesant sur les entreprises, il est donc propos&#x00E9; de supprimer cette surtransposition.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-03-20", "datePublication": "2025-03-20", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "ET", "libelle": "En traitement"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO849474B0481P0D1N001066?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}